{"doc":{"isMarkdown":false,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"preserveAlpha","mdn_url":"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Attribute/preserveAlpha","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p>« <a href=\"/en-US/SVG/Attribute\" title=\"en/SVG/Attribute\">SVG 属性参考</a></p>\n\n<p><code>preserveAlpha</code> 属性表示<a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a> 元素怎样处透明度。</p>\n\n<p>取值为 <code>false</code> 表示 feConvolveMatrix 元素将应用在包括透明度通道的所有的通道。这是默认的选项。</p>\n\n<p>取值为 <code>true</code> 表示 feConvolveMatrix 仅应用在颜色通道。</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"用法","title":"用法","isH3":false,"content":"<table class=\"standard-table\">\n <tbody>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">类别</th>\n   <td>None</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">值</th>\n   <td><code>true</code> | <code>false</code></td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">可变性</th>\n   <td>Yes</td>\n  </tr>\n  <tr>\n   <th scope=\"row\">规范文档</th>\n   <td><a href=\"https://www.w3.org/TR/SVG11/filters.html#feConvolveMatrixElementPreserveAlphaAttribute\" rel=\"external noopener\" class=\"external\">SVG 1.1 (2nd Edition)</a></td>\n  </tr>\n </tbody>\n</table>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"示例","title":"示例","isH3":false,"content":""}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"元素","title":"元素","isH3":false,"content":"<p>下列元素可以使用 <code>preserveAlpha</code> 属性</p>\n\n<ul>\n <li><a href=\"/zh-CN/docs/Web/SVG/Element/feConvolveMatrix\"><code>&lt;feConvolveMatrix&gt;</code></a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"用法","id":"用法"},{"text":"示例","id":"示例"},{"text":"元素","id":"元素"}],"summary":"« SVG 属性参考","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-07-19T02:29:32.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"preserveAlpha","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/preservealpha","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/main/files/zh-cn/web/svg/attribute/preservealp